<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.1">
<l>poṉṉivar mēṉi maraka tattiṉ poṅkiḷañ cōti yakalat tāram</l>
<l>miṉivar vāyil nalvē tamōtum vētiyar vāṉa varāvar tōḻī,</l>
<l>yeṉṉaiyum nōkki yeṉalku lunōkki yēntiḷaṅ koṅkai yumnōk kukiṉṟār</l>
<l>aṉṉaiyeṉ ṉōkku meṉṟañ cukiṉṟē ṉaccōvoruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Gold is his body; the necklace on his chest with a soft glow</l>
<l rend="indent">where emeralds glisten is [like] lightning.</l>
<l>He is a priest who chants the virtuous Vedic on his lips;</l>
<l rend="indent">he is a celestial, [dear] friend.</l>
<l>Having looked at me and looked at my hips, he even looks at</l>
<l rend="indent">my high, young breasts.</l>
<l>I’m afraid, thinking, “What will my mother look at?”</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
